## Start Here

1. `project.yml` - XcodeGen source of truth
2. `Taskfile.yml` - generate, build, and test entry points
3. `{{ project_slug }}/App.swift` - app entry
4. `{{ project_slug }}/DI/DependencyContainer.swift` - dependency wiring
5. `{{ project_slug }}/Navigation/AppRouter.swift` and `Navigation/Route.swift` - auth gate and routing
6. `{{ project_slug }}/Data/Network/APIClient.swift` and `APIEndpoint.swift` - transport layer
7. `{{ project_slug }}/Data/Repository/` - protocol plus implementation repository files
8. `{{ project_slug }}/Data/Storage/TokenStorage.swift` - session persistence
9. `{{ project_slug }}/UI/` - screens, shared UI, and theme

